## Implementation Timeline

**Month 1: Design the stack**
- Audit what you know
- List potential offers (free to $100K+)
- Pick 3-5 offers to build
- Outline each offer

**Month 2: Build Level 2 (Low-ticket)**
- Create template/guide
- Set up sales page
- Launch to your list
- Goal: 10+ sales

**Month 3: Build Level 3 (Mid-ticket)**
- Create course outline
- Record content
- Set up course platform
- Launch to Level 2 customers
- Goal: 5+ sales

**Month 4: Build Level 4 (High-ticket)**
- Refine your service
- Create case studies
- Launch to Level 3 graduates
- Goal: 1-2 sales

**Month 5-6: Launch Level 5 (Premium retainer)**
- Create retainer program
- Pitch to your best clients
- Goal: 1 retainer client

**By Month 6:**
- Free lead magnet (generating leads)
- Level 2: $1,000-$2,000/month
- Level 3: $2,000-$5,000/month
- Level 4: $5,000-$15,000/month
- Level 5: $15,000/month (1 retainer)
- **Total: $23,000-$37,000/month**

Working 20-30 hours/week (sustainable).

