## Getting Started: Your 30-Day Action Plan

**Week 1: Audit your expertise**
- List what you know really well
- List 10 problems you could solve
- Pick the biggest one

**Week 2: Design Level 1 (free)**
- Create free lead magnet
- Set up email signup
- Plan launch sequence

**Week 3: Launch Level 1 + Build Level 2**
- Release free offer
- Start building $47 product (template or guide)

**Week 4: Launch Level 2 + Plan Level 3**
- Sell $47 product
- Plan your mid-ticket course outline

**By day 30:**
- Free offer live (generating leads)
- $47 product selling
- Course outline done
- Revenue pipeline starting

This is offer stacking. Start simple. Expand strategically.

One business. Multiple offers. True wealth.
